Description:
 mx-updater - tray applet to notify of system and application updates
Changes:
 mx-updater (26.05.01mx25+dev02) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium
 .
   * Fix autostart on slow-starting DEs (e.g. Enlightenment at first launch):
     if the systray host is not yet ready after the initial delay, poll
     up to 60s before proceeding. No change on fast DEs where it is already up.
   * History, changelog and log viewers: replace hard-coded font names and
     sizes with the system fixed/general font via QFontDatabase.systemFont,
     so viewers follow the user's system font settings.
